OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778691956
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,FA former high school teacher accused
OL,8,Fof murder denied harming and sexually
OL,9,Fabusing his adopted baby when
OL,10,Fconfronted by officers, a court heard.
OL,12,FJamie Varley, who worked at South
OL,13,FShore Academy school in Blackpool, is
OL,14,Faccused of murdering 13-month-old
OL,15,FPreston Davey.
OL,17,FHis partner, John McGowan-Fazakerley
OL,18,Fis accused of allowing the death of
OL,19,Fthe child, with both accused of sexual
OL,20,Fabuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
