PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778691956
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,FWhen confronted by the officer Jamie
OL,8,FVarley told police in a video
OL,9,Finterview shown to the jury at Preston
OL,10,FCrown Court: "I have not done it. I
OL,11,Fwill fight you 'til the day I die. I
OL,12,Fknow you are wrong. I have not done
OL,13,Fit."
OL,15,FVarley said he had left the child
OL,16,Falone in the bath for three or four
OL,17,Fminutes before he returned and the
OL,18,Fbaby had drowned.
OL,26,@rD@NOUuD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778691956
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,FBut in the police interview officers
OL,8,Fput to him the post-mortem examination
OL,9,Ffindings of Home Office pathologist Dr
OL,10,FAlison Armour.
OL,12,FDr Armour concluded Preston had not
OL,13,Fdrowned but was the victim of "abusive
OL,14,Ftrauma, non-accidental injuries and
OL,15,Fsexual abuse".
OL,17,FJamie Varley, 37, rushed Preston Davey
OL,18,Fto Blackpool Victoria Hospital
OL,19,Funconscious in his arms, a jury at
OL,20,FPreston Crown Court has been told.
OL,26,@uD@_OUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
