PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778691956
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,FMedics worked for nearly an hour to
OL,8,Fresuscitate the child but could not
OL,9,Fsave him.
OL,11,FThe detective put to Varley that the
OL,12,Fpathologist also found the injuries to
OL,13,Fthe baby suggest he was sexually
OL,14,Fassaulted shortly before his death.
OL,16,F"You are absolutely wrong," Varley
OL,17,Freplied.
OL,19,F"Preston was in your care," the
OL,20,Fofficer continued, "What did you do to
OL,21,Fhim?"
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@[O]{D@AOU{D@[O]|D@TOU}D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
