OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,F"Nothing," the defendant replied.
OL,9,FThe post-mortem examination also found
OL,10,Fbruises to Preston's forehead, back of
OL,11,Fthroat, mouth and bottom and bleeding
OL,12,Fin the lungs.
OL,14,FHis cause of death was given as an
OL,15,Fupper airway obstruction, leading to
OL,16,Fhis collapse by a deliberate act of
OL,17,Fsmothering, or an object or objects
OL,18,Finserted into his mouth.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
