CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778691956
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,FThe officer asked Varley: "How do you
OL,8,Fexplain that level of bruising? How
OL,9,Fdoes he have so many bruises?"
OL,11,FVarley said: "No comment,"
OL,13,FThe officer continued, "By prodding
OL,14,Fhim? By poking him?"
OL,16,FThe defendant said, "No,"
OL,18,FThe officer added: "Preston lived for
OL,19,Fone year, one month and 11 days.
OL,26,@oD@[OUqD@^O]sD@NOUsD@ZO]uD@XOUvD@TO]xD@
OL,26,AUOUxD@YO]zD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
