CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778691956
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,F"He was only in your care just less
OL,8,Fthan four months before he was killed.
OL,10,F"There is no evidence of natural
OL,11,Fdisease.
OL,13,F"I'm going to suggest you have killed
OL,14,FPreston."
OL,16,FThe defendant, raising his voice
OL,17,Freplied: "I have not done it. I will
OL,18,Ffight you 'til the day I die. I know
OL,19,Fyou are wrong. I have not done it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOUvD@IO]yD@JOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
