PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778691956
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,FEarlier, the officer put to Varley the
OL,8,Fseries of images and videos taken of
OL,9,FPreston as evidence of alleged cruelty
OL,10,For indecency.
OL,12,FThey included one video lasting 14
OL,13,Fminutes and 31 seconds where Preston
OL,14,Fwas left alone in a bath.
OL,16,FVarley said he set his phone up to
OL,17,Frecord and was on the landing out of
OL,18,Fsight "to see how he reacts to his own
OL,19,Fcompany".
OL,26,@zD@GOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
