OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778691956
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,FVarley was also asked about intimate
OL,8,Fvideos and photos of the child found
OL,9,Fon his phone which prosecutors allege
OL,10,Fare indecent images.
OL,12,FHe told the officers they were
OL,13,Fattempts at "capturing" his child's
OL,14,Flife.
OL,16,FThe defendant told officers: "Unlike
OL,17,Fyou, I don't think about his genitals
OL,18,F24/7.
OL,26,@uD@MOUuD@WO]xD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
