PN,39511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778691956
OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,F"You are making a mountain out of a
OL,8,Fmolehill. It's totally innocent, it's
OL,9,Fridiculous.
OL,11,F"You have got it now as if I'm a
OL,12,Fbloody pervert.
OL,14,F"That's your job I guess."
OL,16,FPreston Crown Court previously heard
OL,17,Fthat Jamie Varley rushed Preston Davey
OL,18,Fto Blackpool Victoria Hospital
OL,19,Funconscious in his arms.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
