OL,3,CTeacher accused of murder told
OL,4,Cofficers 'I will fight you 'til the
OL,5,Cday i die'
OL,7,FMedics worked for nearly an hour to
OL,8,Fresuscitate the child but could not
OL,9,Fsave him.
OL,11,FVarley denies murder, manslaughter,
OL,12,Ftwo counts of assault by penetration,
OL,13,Ffive counts of cruelty to a child,
OL,14,Fgrievous bodily harm, sexual assault
OL,15,Fof a child, 13 counts of taking
OL,16,Findecent photos or videos of a child,
OL,17,Fone of distributing an indecent photo
OL,18,Fof a child, to his co-accused, and one
OL,19,Fof making an indecent photo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
